            {
                "type": "stat_block",
                "subtype": "equipment",
                "name": "Awakened Metal Shot (Awakened Adamantine Shot)",
                "level": 18,
                "price": {
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "subtype": "price",
                    "text": "3,500 gp",
                    "value": 3500,
                    "currency": "gp"
                },
                "text": "The shot is a high-grade adamantine bullet. The awakened adamantine breaks through any resistance. The shot ignores the first 20 resistance a creature has to physical damage, all damage, or piercing or bludgeoning damage. Against a golem or creature who already has a resistance bypassed by adamantine, or a weakness to adamantine, the shot shatters the target's defenses, causing them to become flat-footed for 1 minute instead. Because adamantine is uncommon, this version of awakened metal shot is uncommon even for gunslingers or other characters with access to uncommon guns and bullets from this book.",
